OL,3,CAdvice as region see increase in
OL,4,Cwhopping cough and respiratory
OL,5,Cillnesses
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Health and
OL,8,FSocial Care Partnership is offering
OL,9,Fadvice to combat illness this summer.
OL,11,FThe region has seen an increase in
OL,12,Fpeople admitted to hospitals with
OL,13,Frespiratory illnesses including
OL,14,Fwhooping cough.
OL,16,FNurse Consultant in Health Protection
OL,17,FFiona McKinnon said: "Some of the
OL,18,Fsymptoms that we are seeing are
OL,19,Fsimilar to a cold-like illness;
OL,20,Fsneezing, sore throats along with
OL,21,Fheadaches and all-over body aches.
