OL,3,CAdvice as region see increase in
OL,4,Cwhopping cough and respiratory
OL,5,Cillnesses
OL,7,FPeople are being advised not to visit
OL,8,Fpeople in hospitals or care homes if
OL,9,Fthey have symptoms.
OL,11,FGerms spread easily, so to help
OL,12,Fprotect others always carry a tissue
OL,13,Fand use it toJcapture coughs and
OL,14,Fsneezes.
OL,16,FGerms can live on tissues for several
OL,17,Fhours and should be disposed of as
OL,18,Fsoon as possible.
