OL,7,FGood hand washing can offer protection
OL,8,Fagainst many common viruses which
OL,9,Fcause a range of respiratory and other
OL,10,Finfections.
OL,12,FIt is important to remember that
OL,13,Falcohol gel does not always kill all
OL,14,Fbugs.
